There&#x27;s also Scott Adams&#x27; prng:<p><pre><code>    uint64_t dilbert_rand(void) {
      return 9;
    }
</code></pre>
Another one of my favorites is UNIXv6:<p><pre><code>    int rand(void) {
      static int gorp;
      gorp = (gorp + 625) &amp; 077777;
      return gorp;
    }</code></pre>
